videoSnippet.title: Afraid of the Strongest Move? || Capablanca vs R. Lopez
videoSnippet.description:
Watch Ivanchuk's Immortal https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=e3E40CKXSII

Jose Raul Capablanca vs R Lopez Martinez
Exhibition Game (1914), Buenos Aires ARG, Aug-22 
Bishop's Opening: Vienna Hybrid. Spielmann Attack (C26)

1. e4 e5 2. Bc4 Bc5 3. Nc3 Nf6 4. d3 Nc6 5. Bg5 h6 6. Bh4 g5 7. Bg3 h5 8. h4 g4 9. Qd2 d6 10. Nge2 Qe7 11. O-O a6 12. Nd5! Nd5 13. ed5 Nd4 14. Nd4 Bd4 15. c3 Bb6 16. d4 f6! 17. Rae1 Bd7 18. Bf4 O-O-O 19. Be3 Rde8 20. g3 Kb8 21. b4 Ba4 22. Bb3 Qd7 23. de5 Be3 24. fe3 fe5 25. Rf6 Bb3 26. ab3 Re7 27. Ref1 Rhe8 28. e4 Qb5 29. Ra1! Qd7 30. c4 Rf7 31. Rf7 Qf7 32. Rf1 Qg7 33. Rf5 Rf8 34. Qg5! Qh8 35. Qh5 Qh5 36. Rh5 Rf3 37. Kg2 Rb3 38. Rf5
